column10:
I really liked playing this awesome game! The graphics are so good, and the gameplay is amazing.
The chapters (missions) are very well made and very captivating. Overall, an amazing experience with:
-Masterpiece story;
-Some of the most remarkable characters of all time;
-Good combat and shooting experience;
I really recommend this game!!!

Poor optimization under mid settings, Ryzen 9 5900X, RX 6700XT;
Short story, boring driving / battle system;
Keyboard inputs are not set around left hand area, i.e. not the esc key, not the enter key, not the arrow keys, can't believe this is still happening to games after 2020.

Mafia: Definitive Edition "Remake without the right to legacy"
The first "Mafia the city of lost heaven" was the pearl of that time. However, from a grafhical point of view it could not  compete with the GTA serie. Now if we talk about the need for a remake of this part, then we can see that most of us either did not know about its possible release or were waiting at glance for the trailer that appeared on the internet  on June 13 2020.

PLUSES of the games:
 - good graphics;
 - saving the main gameplay chips, which can be partially attributed to the minus;
 - good dialogue.

Minuses of the games:
 - there are no additional tasks, but there are from the original;
 - the police are still stupid;
 - mechanics of shooting from a car;
 - the price for the same game is high.

FINAL GRADE 8/10
